defaultChair:default You are just about to? 
default              
defaultProfessor Wessely:default I’m just about to. 
default              
defaultDr Fear:default 11% is the overall proportion in our cohort who were violent offenders; that is, they had had a violent offence recorded on the criminal record system. 
